ditional levels for collecting stars)<br></li><li> different enemies on every planet<br></li><li> 4 bosses<br></li><li> funny dialogues with quirky space station workers<br></li><li> this list will be updated soon with more features as I will add it to the game :)</li></ul><br><strong>Please note</strong>: Space Intern is a title that is still in development, any information provided here may be subject to future changes. This page will be updated with more information, and details as content development progress. Thank you for your understanding.",
